## Key Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Recursive** | Handles unlimited nesting depth |
| **Path Tracking** | Shows full key path (e.g., `database.credentials.pass`) |
| **Type Safe** | Proper type hints for IDE support |
| **Two Versions** | Class-based (`DictDiff`) and simple dict return |
| **Production Ready** | Handles edge cases (None values, empty dicts) |

## Security Notes

⚠️ **Untuk konfigurasi sensitif:**
- Jangan log password/secret dalam production
- Mask sensitive values sebelum diff
- Gunakan untuk audit config changes, bukan credential comparison

